headline: Lennar Unveils Two New Home Collections in Anderson Farms Pricing from the mid $200,000s
summary: Lennar, one of the nation's leading homebuilders, today announced two new home collections now available in Anderson Farms, a master-planned community of single-family homes in Maricopa, Arizona. The exclusive collections by Lennar, Dream and Cottage, offer thoughtful home designs at exceptional price points to help homeownership become reality for many - from first-time homeowners to residents of Maricopa seeking quality and value.

thumbnail.caption: Lennar debuts two new single-family home collections at Anderson Farms in Maricopa, Arizona. The Dream and Cottage collections offer seven floorplans with pricing from the mid $200,000s. Pictured above, the Dream Collection features homes from 814 to 1,120 square feet with two to three bedrooms.
